14, so It's a King (13) and an Ace (1).
Now, how did I know that?

00:05:41.360 --> 00:05:45.480
I would say of course in performance well, it could have
been a 7 and a 7, it could have been a 10 and a 4,

00:05:45.500 --> 00:05:48.540
But I don't have 7's among the cards you're
