00:05:48.540 --> 00:05:52.860
There's no other possibilities, when you have six numbers, there are - 6 times 5 over 2,

00:05:52.860 --> 00:05:55.760
which I think is 15 different ways you can add them
up in pairs.

00:05:55.760 --> 00:06:00.980
Usually you'll get some collisions like 1+4 is the same
as 2+3, but with these Fibonacci numbers,

00:06:00.980 --> 00:06:04.080
you never get collisions - You'll get 15 distinct numbers.

